```{r pancreas 32144630, include=FALSE}

PMID_32144630 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32144630', database = 'PubMed')

PubMed_32144630 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32144630$eprint)

doi_32144630 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32144630$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)
```
